channel.title: Basic Renamed Client
channel.description:
Just another basic renamed client base I made for people. Most basic stuff is configured in Configs.java
Hopefully people will use renamed more often now.
[B]Some Features:[/B] 317-377 cache are enabled for it. Censor in chat is off. Added a working ip and port switcher. Added alot of examples in the JFrame. Added my own autocache downloader. Provided 2 links if you don't have any cache for the client. The links are in Configs.java Added HP Over Heads. New context menus... The number colors when you reach 100k 1mill 1bill JFrame of course. Items, objects, and npc list. Theres no cache edits or any customs/recolors.
[B]Download Link:[/B] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/file/nxm2yzceycn/base.zip]http://www.mediafire.com/file/nxm2yzceycn/base.zip[/url]
If you do edit it and decide to release it please make sure to include some credits for me.
Credits off the top of my head: Me - Hardstyle/Openice123 Mitb - Basic Renamed Client Stewie - Menu's Stu - Indent Item Clicking
[B]Pictures:[/B] JMenu Items [IMG]http://i35.tinypic.com/2ro23c0.png[/img] Auto Cache Downloading [IMG]http://i36.tinypic.com/2akjy9i.png[/img] Login Screen Ip and Port Swich Work 100% [IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/16bg2gw.png[/img] Money Colors, 377 Cache, New Contexts Menus (Menus by Stewie) [IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/k0r6eo.png[/img] HP Over Heads [IMG]http://i33.tinypic.com/jj1fdx.png[/img]
